17px;\" textstyle=\"\">PlayStation5 PS5 </span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">游戏机 光驱版值得入手</span></span></span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"微软雅黑\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;mso-color-alt:\nwindowtext;letter-spacing:.4pt;background:white;'><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">改善家庭生活少不了，夏天来了，空调电扇有需要的可以换新了，新款美的空调安排起来</span></span></span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"微软雅黑\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;mso-color-alt:\nwindowtext;letter-spacing:.4pt;background:white;'><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">当然了不能光给自己买，给家里的老婆也要照顾到位，</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">COACH</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">的通勤包和雅诗兰黛的面霜也要准备起来</span></span></span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"background: white;text-align: center;\"><span style='font-size: 9pt;font-family: \"微软雅黑\", sans-serif;color: black;letter-spacing: 0.4pt;background: white;'><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">长按二维码识别，查看同款好物清单</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">👇</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"background: white;text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style='font-size: 9pt;font-family: \"微软雅黑\", sans-serif;color: blue;letter-spacing: 0.4pt;background: white;'><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100013930\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/QDzjsr2LzB7KkXibtVkxtC99RHojCQAz30MPOUzfESBpmXGlLGuKNxhLZzT0YVCqU1TMEicKn0DSX7F2xPaX4HgwSSbbBYwuwickPAd7Rz7RlQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"180\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/QDzjsr2LzB7KkXibtVkxtC99RHojCQAz30MPOUzfESBpmXGlLGuKNxhLZzT0YVCqU1TMEicKn0DSX7F2xPaX4HgwSSbbBYwuwickPAd7Rz7RlQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"width: 378px;height: 378px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">这里分享个更省钱的小技巧：</span></span></p><p><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">打开拼多多APP首页，直接点进百亿补贴专区，一定要关注顶部的“加倍补””消费券“”专属补贴“活动，还有右上角的”百亿补贴会员“也记得点进去，把能领的券全领一遍，百亿补贴叠加券后价格会更香！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">现在正逢618大促补贴力度加码，</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">百亿消费券翻倍发券，618期间至少可领600元券包，</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">包含2张全国消费券和价值468元的地区消费券包。</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">百亿补贴V3会员还能限时领取665元大额券包，单券直减400元，</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">优惠力度太良心了！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">比如iPhone17系列，百亿补贴券后比官网直降千元，同样享受正品保障+全国联保，闭眼冲就对了。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">（活动持续优化中，商品范围、价格请以拼多多APP内显示为准）</span></span></p><p><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">经常有读者后台问多多啥时候有活动，想要买手机，这不机会就来了👇</span></span></p><p style=\"\"><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"微软雅黑\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;color:blue;'><span data-pm-slice='1 1 [\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"p\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\\\"微软雅黑\\\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;color:blue;\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"}]' leaf=\"\"><a class=\"weapp_text_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wx32540bd863b27570\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"拼多多\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/index/index?target_page=%2Fpages%2Fweb%2Fweb%3FspecialUrl%3D1%26src%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmobile.yangkeduo.com%252Fbrand_activity_subsidy.html%253F_pdd_fs%253D1%2526_pdd_tc%253Dffffff%2526_pdd_sbs%253D1%2526refer_channel_from%253Dgdmarketing%2526open_mode%253D0%2526campaign%253Dsubsidy%2526cid%253D2605121041maobidao4474\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-type=\"text\" data-unique-id=\"mpkyd05j-j5e4sc\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;text-decoration: none;\" textstyle=\"\">点击直达【拼多多百亿补贴主会场】</span></a></span></span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"微软雅黑\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;mso-color-alt:\nwindowtext;letter-spacing:.4pt;background:white;'><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">一年又过半，大家想要买的很多，我就不一一列举了，大家直接去百亿补贴主会场去搜想要的就行，不用费心比价，下单就是超级优惠的价格了！</span></span></span></p><p style=\"background: white;\"><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"微软雅黑\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;letter-spacing:.4pt;background:white;'><span leaf=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">点击阅读原文，直达百亿补贴主会场，还有更多补贴好物可直接搜索</span></span></span></p><p><span leaf=\"\"><br/></span></p><mp-sponsor-ad class=\"js_cpc_area js_sponsor_inline_ad res_iframe cpc_iframe\" data-id=\"102722038916\" data-trade-mode=\"1\" js_sponsor_ad=\"\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl&amp;sponsor=1#102722038916\"></mp-sponsor-ad><section><span leaf=\"\"><br/></span></section><p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p></div>",
